## Primary Specifications

### EUROCONTROL SPEC-170 - SWIM Technical Infrastructure Yellow Profile

**Title**: EUROCONTROL Specification for SWIM Technical Infrastructure (TI) Yellow Profile

**Latest Edition**: Version 2.0 (14 July 2025)

**URL**: https://www.eurocontrol.int/publication/eurocontrol-spec-170-eurocontrol-specification-swim-technical-infrastructure-ti-yellow

**Purpose**: Contains requirements for system interfaces (protocols) and IT infrastructure capabilities for reliable, secure and efficient information exchange in SWIM context.

**Key Coverage**:
- Service Interface Bindings (WS-Light, AMQP Messaging)
- Security requirements (TLS 1.2, mTLS, authentication)
- Infrastructure capabilities (NTP, overload protection, audit)
- Compliance requirements (SWIM-TIYP-XXXX)

**Citation Format**:
```
EUROCONTROL, "EUROCONTROL SPEC-170: SWIM Technical Infrastructure Yellow Profile", Version 2.0, July 2025.
Available: https://www.eurocontrol.int/publication/eurocontrol-spec-170
```

